author: The Irreverent Reverend
description: I\'m glad to hear that you came home and you\'re OK! I was really missing your weekly videos the last few weeks and was actually becoming quite concerned for you. Hang in there! I live in the "States" and am jealous of how Canada is more prepared than we are. However, I\'m confident we\'ll all get through this..... If we work together! I hope you still continue to make videos and that you are not discouraged by some of your latest video viewership numbers. You definitely have something to share with the world! Thank you for sharing and keep up the good work!

author: Tori Landry
description: Hey thank you! Yes the last couple were a bit rough but I know that comes with the territory.
